name: UI Checklist
description:
101 things to consider when designing an interface, use it to check if your design work is perfect.


This file is only available to Shift Nudge subscribers. Please go to the official website to subscribe for free to get the original version and then see the Figma version.


This file adds operable interactive components on the basis of the original Notion file. The interactive elements made by viggo.

Many of the content is not exactly the same as the original content. Corresponding changes have been made according to understanding.


You can read it against the original version.
